<title>特朗普签署涉TikTok行政令，外交部回应</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%AD%BE%E7%BD%B2%E6%B6%89TikTok%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E4%BB%A4%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%94</link>
